description: [``botocore``] Update lexv2-models client to latest version
[``botocore``] This release adds support for managed rule groups.

[``botocore``] This release adds tagging supports to Route53 Recovery Control Configuration. New APIs: TagResource, UntagResource and ListTagsForResource. Updates: add optional field `tags` to support tagging while calling CreateCluster, CreateControlPanel and CreateSafetyRule.
[``botocore``] Adds waiters support for internet gateways.
[``botocore``] This release adds SMS discontinuation information to the API and CLI references.

[``botocore``] Amazon Route 53 domain registration APIs now support filtering and sorting in the ListDomains API, deleting a domain by using the DeleteDomain API and getting domain pricing information by using the ListPrices API.
[``botocore``] Adds the ability to specify Savings Plans hourly commitments using five digits after the decimal point.
